{"tid":1442654,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【明周封面故事】關智斌迷惘時刻基仔陪玩","createTime":"2019-08-11T04:23:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T05:37:25.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9763661d6bc95244f0a10d05071a601de2eaa016","tid":1442654,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:23:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mc3FKaR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMc3FKaR.jpg&h=77cf2fb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 關智斌 Kenny Kwan（Kenny）被形象破產的 張致恒Stevencheung（Steven）拖累，一度紅館夢碎，Steven被揭多角戀時，與Kenny身在泰國拍演唱會宣傳片，Boy&rsquo;z的銀色旅途是從布吉出發，想不到亦在這裏終結，猶幸塞翁失馬，Kenny最終以個人身份踏上紅館舞台，好友 古巨基 Leo Ku、 容祖兒 Joey Yung、 張敬軒 Hins Cheung和  Twins 蔡卓妍&amp;鍾欣潼 全面力撐演出，Kenny提到跟他們的珍貴友情，一度哽咽，「我在group內說：『願意一世做牛做馬』。」"},{"pid":"5cbe17215639e115b85b863e8f3fee29a6de1648","tid":1442654,"uid":76098,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:27:00.000Z","msg":"粒lin好似深色左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b2aef4e8049b7d209159a1c8eee7ac28fe1f90c","tid":1442654,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:27:27.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">721元朗恐襲</span></strong></span></div><br />\n警黑合作, 警署落閘, <br />\n999唔通,無人落charge<br />\n<br />\n721元朗恐襲第22日<br />\n無人落charge <br />\n無警停職<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無忘721<br />\n記者請日日追問插問</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">大家copy and paste pls<br />\n每日改第xx日<br />\n<br />\nKeep push to keep this at the top!</span></span>"},{"pid":"d6b9eddd601f25e589681cb8c5a8d2fac1b4623d","tid":1442654,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:32:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7XjQ517.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https